                <span class="verdict-icon">🔗</span>
                <div><strong>Different purpose.</strong> CEP engines run in production to react to patterns. Daisy Chains runs in test to validate patterns. If the platform uses CEP rules, Daisy Chains validates that rules fire correctly.</div>
